<section class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
  <div class="reviews-inner">

    <div class="reviews-head reveal">
      <span class="reviews-eyebrow">Verified reviews</span>
      <h2 class="reviews-title">What people are <span class="reviews-title-accent">saying.</span></h2>
      <div class="reviews-summary" aria-label="Average rating 4.8 out of 5 from verified purchases">
        <div class="reviews-stars" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>&#9733;</span><span>&#9733;</span><span>&#9733;</span><span>&#9733;</span><span>&#9733;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-summary-text">
          <strong>4.8</strong> out of 5 &middot; Verified purchases
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <article class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">&ldquo;Didn&rsquo;t expect to feel this calm at 7am&rdquo;</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I bought this mostly for the gua sha but the full routine genuinely became my <strong>favourite five minutes of the day</strong>. <strong>Jawline looks tighter after three weeks</strong>, and the ice roller in the morning is unreal for de-puffing after bad sleep. Packaging felt <strong>way more premium than the price</strong>. The only &ldquo;downside&rdquo; is I now guilt-trip myself if I skip a day.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Sofia M.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">&#10003; Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Complete Ritual</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">&ldquo;The ice roller alone is worth it&rdquo;</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I&rsquo;ve tried the viral ones from Amazon and they always <strong>leaked or smelled like plastic</strong>. This one <strong>actually holds the cold</strong>, feels solid in your hand, and <strong>doesn&rsquo;t drip</strong>. I use it every morning after coffee and my under-eyes look like I <strong>slept eight hours</strong> (I did not). Instant fix on hangover mornings too, not that I&rsquo;d know.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Jess R.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">&#10003; Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Ice Roller</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="review-stars" aria-label="4 out of 5 stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<span class="star-dim">&#9733;</span></div>
        <h3 class="review-title">&ldquo;Skeptical husband, now he steals mine&rdquo;</h3>
        <p class="review-body">Bought this thinking it was another skincare gimmick. <strong>Two weeks in</strong>, my <strong>cheekbones look more defined</strong> and my <strong>jaw tension from grinding at night</strong> is <strong>noticeably better</strong>. I follow the little guide they include and do it with the rosehip oil. Four stars only because I wish it came in a pouch &mdash; I&rsquo;m paranoid about dropping the stone. Otherwise perfect.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Amelia T.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">&#10003; Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Amethyst Gua Sha</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">&ldquo;Rosehip oil that actually absorbs&rdquo;</h3>
        <p class="review-body">I have combination skin and oils usually terrify me. This one <strong>sinks in within a minute</strong> and <strong>doesn&rsquo;t leave that greasy film</strong>. My <strong>dark spots from old acne are fading faster</strong> than with the $45 one I was using before. Bottle is small but <strong>a few drops is all you need</strong> &mdash; I&rsquo;m six weeks in and barely made a dent.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Priya K.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">&#10003; Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Rosehip Oil</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
        <h3 class="review-title">&ldquo;Bought for my mum, stole it back&rdquo;</h3>
        <p class="review-body">Ordered this as a birthday gift and <strong>ended up buying a second one for myself</strong> the next week. The roller is <strong>so relaxing after screen time</strong> that I&rsquo;ve replaced my evening phone scroll with it. My <strong>skin looks less tired</strong>, <strong>I fall asleep faster</strong>, and honestly it just feels like a <strong>little ritual of self-respect</strong>. Exactly what the name promises.</p>
        <footer class="review-meta">
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="review-name">Laura D.</span>
            <span class="review-verified" aria-label="Verified purchase">&#10003; Verified</span>
          </div>
          <div class="review-product">Complete Ritual</div>
        </footer>
      </article>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-section {
    background: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
    padding: 112px 80px;
  }
  .reviews-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .reviews-head {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
  }
  .reviews-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta, #A15E3C);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .reviews-title {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }
  .reviews-title-accent {
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
  }

  .reviews-summary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    background: var(--white, #FDFAF5);
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .reviews-stars {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 2px;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .reviews-summary-text {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--stone, #6B5A40);
  }
  .reviews-summary-text strong {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: var(--white, #FDFAF5);
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .review-stars {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--terracotta, #B8704A);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .review-stars .star-dim {
    color: var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
  }
  .review-title {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 1.6vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
    line-height: 1.28;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .review-body {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--stone, #6B5A40);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .review-meta {
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
  }
  .review-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .review-name {
    font-family: var(--serif), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
  }
  .review-verified {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta, #A15E3C);
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .review-product {
    font-family: var(--sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--stone, #6B5A40);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .reviews-section {
      padding: 80px 32px;
    }
    .reviews-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .review-card {
      padding: 32px 28px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .reviews-section {
      padding: 64px 20px;
    }
    .reviews-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .review-card {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
    .review-title {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .reviews-summary {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Customer Reviews",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Customer Reviews" }]
}
{% endschema %}
